snippet.title: Umbral Core - EVO Preview
snippet.description:
An extensive early preview for Umbral Core's gameplay, art direction, features and more. World premiered during the EVO 2022 Showcase!

The game is currently in pre-alpha development and we plan to launch a Kickstarter campaign later this year, as well as a playable open alpha.

Follow us for more:
Discord: https://discord.gg/VQy62c7njv
Twitter: https://twitter.com/UmbralCore
website: https://umbralcore.com/
